2. Determine the ‘ename’, ‘job’, ‘sal’ rename the title as Job-sal the output must be Job-Sal as
SMITH [CLERK] RS.2000
SQL> select ename||' '||'['||job||']'||' '||'Rs.'||sal as job_sal from emp;

